{"tid":137870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲海灘開心遛狗 愛犬竟被鯊魚一口咬走","createTime":"2017-02-28T07:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T10:58:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0fc32ab555aa624a7e849d89f62d6f9967d9ef0","tid":137870,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVoVMqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVoVMqp.jpg&h=fc7a4ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有飼主在澳洲海灘遛狗，愛犬卻被鯊魚咬走。（圖擷自《雪梨先鋒報》）</span><br />\n2017-02-28  13:45<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕澳洲雪梨南部科內爾半島（Kurnell）上，有著吸引大批觀光人潮的美麗海灘，不過當奈吉爾（Nigel）帶著愛犬「莫莉」（Molly）到海灘遊玩時，卻有1隻鯊魚將走入海水中的狗狗一口咬走，讓飼主嚇傻在當地。<br />\n據《雪梨先鋒報》報導，當時奈吉爾正在和莫莉玩「你丟我撿」的遊戲，過程中他將木棍丟到淺攤上，沒想到因為退潮的緣故木棍隨著海水退得有點快，距離岸邊約5公尺遠，狗狗仍舊開心地衝過去想咬著木棍還給主人，此時突然有1隻身長3.5公尺的鯊魚現身，叼著莫莉直接潛回海裡。<br />\n目睹愛犬被鯊魚吃掉的奈吉爾受到極大的創傷，呢喃著他當時做什麼也無法保護到莫莉。現在管轄科內爾半島的薩瑟蘭郡議會已經公告，要求遊客不要進入周圍水域，並且所有飼主都要確保自己的寵物遠離海邊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1988691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1988691&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDLwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=abb847e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1988691&h=4ee58ce2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1988691</a>"},{"pid":"116106e3aa77a99451b5335d237492a98a1ab029","tid":137870,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"秒"},{"pid":"e3023ed1d6c4e39079b430d2cb4f502d00b1cb96","tid":137870,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb2899a2691a28f897ff0bece29e3eb339f33d7","tid":137870,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"納dee 扮鯊魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53966ab179da65879ab46de52c4bdcc7d591ad0f","tid":137870,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"474fc1d0737e6a9e69a2fe50e1e96f8df4a02672","tid":137870,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58d2cbccd02385eba468c54003d65237829ad54","tid":137870,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b7e12e81d181357d6d7472706e495052beda33","tid":137870,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"果到水好清, 成日有人落水. 我真係好懷疑係咪有沙魚."},{"pid":"597a2e8955a51685bde64d7e9d4a9eea918a208c","tid":137870,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2916139bb2a376f6e2a7768213f92fde5fcf67","tid":137870,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}